{
  "texts": [
    "We use the topic assignment described in Subsubsection IV-A5 to label the clusters.",
    "For clusters, we use the centroid of the approximated polygon to position the label.",
    "When a cluster is expanded, the subclusters within need to be clearly labeled as well.",
    "Using the centroid of the sub-cluster as the label position is not a good choice because the label would cause a serious cluttering issue.",
    "Therefore, for a sub-cluster, we first calculate its centroid C s ub."
  ]
}